{"tid":743631,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過前度同現任握手？","createTime":"2018-07-15T14:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T01:01:57.000Z","uid":121544,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1fb371d5c385fe1735485812672f231430f9a7","tid":743631,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:13:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n前排返酒吧，好多年前既前度冇啦啦上左嚟飲酒撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一見到我就全程挨住我又攬下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後現任冇啦啦又上左嚟接我收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我前度就攬住我同我現任握手兼自我介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個場面真係好老懢<br />\n<br />\n雖然後尾我拆掂左，但有時佢一聽到握手依個字眼就會又提返件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cded2b31b19d65ebf0f62e570df860bcc3f1d8","tid":743631,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/222448_ab34c36e7a72ad58c8aed964a519df7b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F222448_ab34c36e7a72ad58c8aed964a519df7b.gif&h=9321f1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個一齊討論你"},{"pid":"1d470e8e619d4eb8d01b2293151bd2d450d10329","tid":743631,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cded2b31b19d65ebf0f62e570df860bcc3f1d8","tid":743631,"uid":10277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/222448_ab34c36e7a72ad58c8aed964a519df7b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F222448_ab34c36e7a72ad58c8aed964a519df7b.gif&h=9321f1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個一齊討論你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"依個你唔會知咖嘛"},{"pid":"550a